## 7. Очистка кэша (опционально)

### `DELETE /cache/{type}`

**Path parameter:** type = all | summary | flashcards | quiz

**Response (200 OK):**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "cleared": "summary, flashcards, quiz",
  "keys_removed": 42
}
```

