## Сводная таблица эндпоинтов

| Method | Endpoint | Request | Response |
|--------|----------|---------|----------|
| GET | /health | — | статус |
| POST | /upload/file | multipart | текст из файла |
| POST | /summary | {text/topic} | {summary} |
| POST | /flashcards | {text, num_cards} | {flashcards[]} |
| POST | /quiz | {text, num_questions} | {quiz[]} |
| POST | /export/pdf | {title, content} | PDF file |
| DELETE | /cache/{type} | — | статистика очистки |

